title: What Self-Care Means to Us
description:
Before you can take care of others, you have to take care of yourself. This week, Camo and Tasia talk about how they decompress and take care of themselves, whether it's a day at the spa or just curling up with a good book. They also discuss their religious beliefs and how you can't just place them in a simple box of "Christian."
